title: Roman Frescoes from Boscoreale (Art Ebook)
description:
Roman Frescoes from Boscoreale: The Villa of Plubius Fannius Synistor in Reality and Virtual Reality

Metropolitan | 2010 | ISBN: 0300155190 | English | PDF | 50 pages | 32.42 Mb

When Mount Vesuvius erupted in a.d. 79, burying much of the region around the Bay of Naples in lava, one of the extraordinary Roman villas thereby preserved was that of P. Fannius Synistor at Boscoreale. Its discovery in 1899 revealed breathtaking wall paintings that were dispersed in 1903
